{"id": "1341084189331820614", "channel_id": "1341084189331820614", "type": 0, "author_id": "594196021119287316", "author_name": "nemu_s_t_a_r", "author_bot": false, "content": "目前明顯BUG:\n諾 非因特 反轉傷仍是100%，並非正常觸發20%。\n\n建議修改:\n血希明顯過強，建議出血比照毒反定上限。 \n旺達 鯊魚 米粒 環拉 降力與偷力 砍%數數值，或訂個上限。", "timestamp": "2025-02-17T16:29:46.876000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "😡", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}, {"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 13}, {"emoji": "😅", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}, {"emoji": "👎", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1341084189331820614", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "星辰篇角色問題", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1181168158678204497"]}
